id: "class:warpriest#cult_leader"
name: "Cult Leader"
description: "Referred to as fanatics, lunatics, or obsessives, cultists see themselves\
  \ as genuine devotees of their deity. And the hierarchs of those devotees, the cult\
  \ leaders, are the most fanatical of them all. Cult leaders are known for turning\
  \ reasonable hearts toward corrupted teachings and striking at those that get in\
  \ the way of their agenda."
