- id: "ability:hide_in_plain_sight#warpriest_cult_leader"
  name: "Hide in Plain Sight"
  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 12th level, a cult leader can use the Stealth skill even while\
    \ being observed. As long as he is within 10 feet of an area of dim light, a cult\
    \ leader can hide himself from view in the open without anything to actually hide\
    \ behind. He cannot, however, hide in his own shadow."
